<body class="index-body"> <!-- Class for background -->
    <header>
        <h1>7/8/9 Theme Park - Relive the Magic of the 70s, 80s, and 90s!</h1>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/areas">Areas</a>
        <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="/attractions">Attractions</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <section class="index-container">
            <h2>A Trip Down Memory Lane</h2>
            <p>
                Step into a world where the best of the 70s, 80s, and 90s come to life! 
                The 7/8/9 Theme Park is a nostalgic journey through three of the most iconic decades, 
                where music, fashion, and thrilling rides collide to create the ultimate retro experience.
            </p>

            <h2>Our Iconic Attractions</h2>
            <div class="attractions-grid">
                <!-- 70s Attractions -->
                <div class="attraction-70s">
                    <h3>The Groovy 70s</h3>
                    <p>
                        Get your bell-bottoms on and dive into the funky disco-themed roller coaster! 
                        The 70s section also includes a retro ferris wheel with stunning park views and 
                        groovy tunes to take you back in time.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- 80s Attractions -->
                <div class="attraction-80s">
                    <h3>The Radical 80s</h3>
                    <p>
                        Relive the arcade era with neon lights, fast-paced action, and thrilling rides like 
                        the Synthwave Racer. Don’t miss the Laser Tag arena that brings the 80s vibe back 
                        with a futuristic twist!
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- 90s Attractions -->
                <div class="attraction-90s">
                    <h3>The Extreme 90s</h3>
                    <p>
                        Feel the adrenaline with the grunge-inspired roller coaster that’ll leave you 
                        breathless! The 90s skate park attraction and a VR experience let you dive deep into 
                        the coolest moments of the decade.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Nostalgic Carousel/Banner -->
            <div class="carousel">
                <!-- You could implement an image carousel with retro images -->
                <img src="/images/retro-park-1.jpg" alt="Retro Park Attraction 1">
                <img src="/images/retro-park-2.jpg" alt="Retro Park Attraction 2">
                <img src="/images/retro-park-3.jpg" alt="Retro Park Attraction 3">
            </div>

        </section>
    </main>
